Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:07.94,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,At the police academy,\Nclassmates strengthen their bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:11.99,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,by competing against \Nand supporting one another
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:16.01,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,under class flags they design themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.33,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious clouds block your field of view!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:21.16,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Clear them away with deductive \Nreasoning and the sky sparkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.07,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dark shadows loom in Morofushi's past!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:25.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is uncovered \Nby the power of his classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.80,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:47.72,AcademyArc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,1)}Police Academy Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:18.99,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)}Police Academy Arc Wild Police Story \NCASE. Morofushi Hiromitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Police Academy Arc Wild Police \NStory CASE. Morofushi Hiromitsu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:21.24,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:24.87,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(344,314)\fad(360,351)\3c&H8D5852&}Matsuda Jinpei (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.07,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How is the bathroom this dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.54,DCMain,WATARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:31.94,DCMain,WATARU,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}every class got covered in mud practicing \Nfor the sports festival this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:30.00,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(401,351)\pos(322,314)\3c&HAA6460&}Date Wataru (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:35.05,DCMain,WATARU,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, they practiced \Nin the rain yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:40.84,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}By the way, your design for \Nour class flag was really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.51,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H9F7066&\fad(359,351)\pos(352,314)}Furuya Rei (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.63,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:45.35,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,394)\pos(417,315)\3c&H9D6663&}Morofushi Hiromitsu (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:46.68,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I kind of thought a cherry blossom design \Nfor a police academy would be cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:50.41,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It was finished and delivered \Nthis morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.31,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(360,390)\pos(205,314)\3c&HA37171&}Hagiwara Kenji (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.49,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.98,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.07,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimesNewRoman\fs26\fad(438,1)\pos(240,130)\shad0\c&H04020D&\3c&H017EC8&\bord3\b1}Onizuka's Class
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.07,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimesNewRoman\b1\fs30\pos(134,220)\shad0\bord3\fad(438,1)}Cherry Blossoms in Full Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:58.07,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! I've been keeping it \Non me at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.04,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,The colors are great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:00.97,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.07,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited for the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.33,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.48,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Cat paw prints?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.08,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,They kind of stink, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:14.21,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I was hanging it out a window so \NI could show it off to the other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.96,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Not only was it blown away by the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:22.37,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,but a stray cat that had stepped \Nin crap walked all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.51,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,It pissed me off, so I got Hagi \Nto help me try to catch the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.97,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That's how this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.94,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what the cat was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:37.44,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,And when I sent it to the cleaners, \NOnizuka called us into his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.52,DCItalic,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sure you've noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.91,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(357,354)\pos(326,296)\3c&HAA675A&}Onizuka Hachizo (48)\NRookie Class Instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:43.91,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but I've received complaints \Nfrom the other instructors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.58,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,They say that recently the bathroom \Nhas been unbelievably filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.18,DCFlashback,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not just our—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.78,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:54.96,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that the five of you will be \Ncleaning the bathroom every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.18,DCFlashback,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.64,DCFlashback,REI,0000,0000,0000,,I-Instructor Onizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.42,DCFlashback,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a bit unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:03.70,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? I thought I'd give you \Nboys a chance to make up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.85,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,for all the mischief you've \Ncommitted until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.66,DCFlashback,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.64,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:14.56,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,for one week, the five of you will be \Ncleaning the bathroom and changing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.13,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're dismissed. Now get to it.
