Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.71,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a photo of a young girl \Nwho was reported missing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.96,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,last night in this jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:36.83,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't return home after \Ngoing out to run an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.38,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Morofushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.61,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:46.14,DCFlashback,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I've just seen her \Naround the city before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:48.74,DCFlashback,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,May I take this with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.67,DCFlashback,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I might recall something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.14,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:57.28,DCFlashback,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you finish cleaning \Nby bath time at 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.65,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.53,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,how long are we going to keep doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:05.36,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we talk about something \Nmore exciting while we clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.95,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.37,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Morofushi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:15.12,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You know something about that missing \Ngirl you were looking at, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.38,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.57,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:20.85,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make sense for you to react like \Nthat if you'd only seen her around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:26.38,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,She looks just like a girl \NI used to play with as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:30.64,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,She passed away due to an illness, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.64,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,But it caught my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:37.44,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,If she was a childhood friend, \Ndoes that mean I've met her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.31,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I knew her when I lived in Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.51,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:43.88,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.32,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,We're all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:47.82,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.75,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's not an interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.16,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, c'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.86,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:04.42,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Zero told me to wait until you \Nbrought it up so I'd been holding back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:10.09,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,but you're looking for the guy \Nwho killed your parents, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:15.36,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gloomy because that missing \Ngirl looks like your childhood friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.39,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,and reminded you of the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.77,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.77,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's true. You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:26.82,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I have to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.08,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to drag anyone else into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:32.28,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone else died because of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.41,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,We won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.41,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Together we've been through...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.12,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty of dangerous situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.75,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,But with the five of us together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:43.88,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,We've made it through somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.23,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,So tell us, Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:49.17,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.73,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,"You can trust us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.60,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like something \Na bad guy would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.35,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.79,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,about the incident \Nthat took place 15 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.61,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,that froze the hands of the clock inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:11.11,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That terrifying night \Nenveloped by the smell of iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:21.78,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,He arrived around 7PM when I was \Neating dinner with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.91,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,The visitor apparently knew my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:30.63,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and I could hear them speaking \Ncalmly in the entryway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.00,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,But the man began raising his voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.39,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and when my mother went to the entryway \Nto see what was going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.65,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard my father scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.55,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and my mother who'd gone pale with fear \Nreturned to the dining room and told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:46.70,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,"Hide in here for a while."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.11,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't come out until I tell you it's safe."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.40,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Then she shut me inside \Na Japanese-style closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.03,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her arguing with the man next,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.79,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,but eventually I stopped \Nhearing her voice as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.22,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and the iron-like smell \Nof blood began to fill the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:05.46,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Even I could smell it from inside the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.51,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.68,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.95,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,A song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:17.92,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It wasn't my father's \Nor mother's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.99,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,In a fake high-pitched and wheedling voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.81,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,he sang the same phrase over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:29.57,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,So I cautiously peered through \Na gap in the closet door
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:33.69,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and saw a man holding \Na bloody knife humming,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.57,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,"It's all right now. Come on out."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.40,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What about his face? Did you see his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:45.08,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No. I was too scared to look at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:49.05,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,But why was he looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.26,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.59,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,He called a girl's name \Nafter he said "come on out."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.86,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the girl \NI often played with as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.35,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,The one who looked exactly like \Nthe girl reported missing last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.27,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.27,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he be looking \Nfor her at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.65,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,What's her family name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:15.68,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I only ever called her by her given name, \Nso I don't remember her family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.78,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we were first-year \Ngrade school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:21.79,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't see the culprit's face, \Nbut you saw his tattoo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:26.74,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He slipped in the blood \Nand bumped into
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:30.06,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,the Japanese-style closet \NI was hiding inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:34.55,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,When he moved away from \Nthe closet, for a moment I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:38.55,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,the goblet-shaped tattoo on his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.93,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that tattoo \Nwas on his shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.34,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.34,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,After he moved away from the closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.53,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,he held his shoulder \Nas though he was in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:54.29,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see the tattoo anymore because \Nit was hidden behind his bloody hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.85,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,So, what'd he do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:10:01.95,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. At some point, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:06.76,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I was woken by the sound of doors \Nbeing opened and closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:09.83,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,As I was bracing myself \Nfor being discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.75,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,the closet door was opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:16.68,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hiromitsu, our parents are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.53,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.15,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,...by my older brother who had \Nreturned from his camp school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:28.38,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It was the next afternoon. \NI'd been asleep for half the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:30.42,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You have an older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:33.35,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently a capable officer \Nfor the Nagano police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:35.78,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,They call him Komei of Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:40.27,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you tell your brother \Nabout the tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:43.62,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No. After that, not only did \NI suffer some minor amnesia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.62,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,from the trauma of the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.79,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,but I also lost my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:51.94,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was taken in by relatives \Nin Nagano, while I went to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.67,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was living somewhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.42,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't regain my voice until I met Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.55,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,So you joined the police academy so \Nyou could catch your parents' killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.39,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Recently I've been remembering a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.88,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about \Nreviewing the circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.34,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,from the perspective of a police officer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.94,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and telling my brother what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:18.82,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,And while conducting your search, \Nyou encountered three suspicious men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:20.90,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:24.87,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,We already talked to the \Nthree of them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:25.81,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.59,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:27.82,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:29.56,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,We split up and questioned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.21,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,To help you get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:37.21,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,How did you even know I'm looking \Nfor the man who killed my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.31,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:43.61,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,You're always looking up the stabbing \Ndeaths of a couple in Nagano online.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:48.22,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've heard details \Nabout the culprit and the tattoo, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.62,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's unlikely the culprit \Nis here in Tokyo instead of Nagano
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:56.36,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and just happens to be in my vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.00,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.11,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,It's also just a coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:04.61,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,that the missing girl looks just like \Nyour childhood friend from 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.65,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what you'd normally think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:11.50,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's your intuition telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.09,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.70,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel some kind of uneasiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.45,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.38,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.21,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Team Leader, we'll start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.35,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.14,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Team Leader, we'll start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.19,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I had a tough time since \Nhe wasn't much of a talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:37.56,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}His name is Irie Sumio, 46 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:39.36,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,394)\pos(322,314)\3c&H792E3D&}Irie Sumio (46)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.62,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He lives with his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.61,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He got the tattoo on his \Nshoulder ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.49,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It's apparently the champion's cup he won
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.28,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,at a neighborhood association \Nping pong tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.89,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:49.53,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.16,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Also, he told his wife, \N"hana ya mizu wo kure kure."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:57.20,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it wasn't \N"hana ni mizu wo kuretekure?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.65,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:02.05,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nagano dialect. They say "kureru" \Ninstead of "ageru" for watering flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.79,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:07.95,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,But if he got the tattoo ten years ago, \Nthe math doesn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.31,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Hagi, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:11.93,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:16.34,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tomori Hajime, 50 years old. He lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.65,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(315,313)\3c&H994152&\pos(355,315)}Tomori Hajime (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:22.18,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He still operates the cleaning service \Nhe inherited from his uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:27.78,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,He got the goddess Kannon tattooed \Non his upper arm 20 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.08,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,for the wife and mother he lost \Nin a traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.98,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,He graduated with an engineering degree
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.46,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,and often performed repairs \Non simple electric appliances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.22,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Because they're from the same region,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.21,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,he apparently played doubles \Nin ping pong with Irie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:50.09,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,If he got the tattoo 20 years ago, \Nthat doesn't conflict with the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:54.10,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not sure how you can \Nmistake a Kannon tattoo for a goblet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.79,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of things that look like goblets,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:14:02.38,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the bike shop employee was named \NMonobe Shuzo, 35 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.86,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(271,349)\3c&H792E3D&\pos(321,315)}Monobe Shuzo (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.55,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like Tomori, he lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.09,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,He got a scorpion tattooed \Non the back of his neck
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:12.26,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,when he was around 20 years old, \Nso that's barely 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:15.07,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's on the back of his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.58,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.33,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't seem right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.00,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.28,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Morofushi? You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:32.01,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The other day, I called my brother \Nto tell him what I'd managed to recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.01,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking quick returns is shortsighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:40.26,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me seeking fast returns \Nbefore you have the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.23,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't hiding \Nin a Japanese-style closet then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.51,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,but a Western-style closet \Nwith double folding doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:50.78,DCItalic,TAKAAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That was a western-style house without \NJapanese-style closets and sliding doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.28,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,...and remembered that he told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.79,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, are you sure you're not mixing it up \Nwith your home in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:01.79,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,That house was old and only had \NJapanese-style closets and sliding doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.29,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.72,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's weird, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.84,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,If you were hiding inside a Western-style \Ncloset with double folding doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.80,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,the doors should've closed \Nwhen the culprit bumped into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.50,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:20.31,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,For you to see the culprit holding his \Nshoulder, you'd have to reopen the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.79,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you open the doors \Nunder those circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.45,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:32.93,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe the gap you were peering \Nthrough was wide instead of tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:36.87,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You can see what's happening outside \Nthrough the slits in a closet door
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.83,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,even when the doors are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.92,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:49.17,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the culprit through \Nthe slits in the closet door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.18,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,If I couldn't see up or down \Nbecause of the slits,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:57.43,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,then Tomori-san's Kannon tattoo \Ncould also look like a goblet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:02.33,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,And if Tomori's from the same place \Nas Irie, who speaks Nagano dialect,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.69,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,then it's gotta be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:08.69,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,The man who killed your parents \N15 years ago was Tomori Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.24,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.87,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered Yuri-chan's full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.86,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Then was she his...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:23.85,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,On a school trip, Yuri-chan \Nsuddenly got a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:29.02,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,My father, who was a teacher, \Nrushed her to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:32.01,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,but her appendicitis was acute \Nand it was already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:36.56,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,If Tomori-san couldn't \Naccept his daughter's death
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.10,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,and thought my father had \Nkidnapped Yuri-chan, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.62,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.83,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,According to Hagi's investigation, \NTomori-san lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.11,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,But when we were trapped inside \Nthe convenience store during the robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:52.61,DCItalic,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I came to get snacks for my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:58.37,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible a similar-looking \Ngirl went missing because...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.50,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:06.00,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\fnArial\bord2\shad3\c&HF9F9FE&\3c&HE5BC6B&\4c&HA17E72&\pos(12,12)}Tomori Cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.00,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,the man himself about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.88,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.13,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.98,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Is he closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.13,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.72,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.09,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.02,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:26.24,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It looks like it's connected \Nto the other washing machines,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:29.44,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,so it might flatten \Nthe entire shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:33.48,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,This one on the right end \Nseems to be the source,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:35.42,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,so we should be fine \Nif we can stop this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.72,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.21,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Matsuda, you disarm the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.53,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Zero and Hagiwara, \Nevacuate the local residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:46.05,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Morofushi and I will look for Tomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.87,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:51.37,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are injured, so I can't \Ndo precise work right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.09,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hagiwara can take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.51,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could say you can count on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.66,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,but that cat actually scratched me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.72,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.79,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.06,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Y-You want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.39,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you'd be good with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.17,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.48,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you guys to disarm the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.33,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.44,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori-san, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.69,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:24.80,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Tomori—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:30.63,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout. She finally fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:36.05,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,You and dad are about to go \Non a little trip, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.68,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.01,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,That wire is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.05,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.07,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Impatience is the greatest trap of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.06,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.44,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That girl isn't Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.82,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.92,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who made us meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:54.98,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:59.99,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I didn't kill you while \Nyou were sleeping in the closet that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:04.81,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,You were friends with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:10.87,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,I knew if I followed you, you'd someday \Nlead me to wherever your parents hid Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.38,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Now step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:20.76,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd originally intended to depart at 4:30PM \Ntoday when Yuri was born, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:25.76,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the day \Nof the trip, Yuri-chan mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.95,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,that she'd had an argument with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.56,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,That she'd told you she was \Nnever going back to that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.95,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\fnArial\bord2\shad3\c&HF9F9FE&\3c&HE5BC6B&\4c&HA17E72&\frz15.23\fsp7\move(150,145,120,145)\t(1,3695,1\fsp10}Tomori Cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.46,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:54.83,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why won't it explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.84,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,They disarmed it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.09,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,After that, Yuri-chan told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:09.36,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,"When I get home from this trip, \NI need to apologize to my dad."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.02,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:21.68,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man. I wasted my time \Nevacuating everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.79,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.70,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:33.21,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's 4:29PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:38.59,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, kid. I'll apologize to your parents \Nonce I'm on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.21,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.47,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! He rigged the second floor, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.01,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.47,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Morofushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.72,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.76,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.72,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.06,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Out front, the cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:52.93,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:00.98,DCItalic,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,The next time I inhale, \Nthe smoke will destroy my lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:05.91,DCItalic,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to shout a warning \Nor see what's happening outside, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:10.56,DCItalic,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I trust them to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.61,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Let me die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.80,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:28.26,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be paying for your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.10,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.08,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You just {\i1}happened{\i0} \Nto find the kidnapped girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:00.56,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,just {\i1}happened{\i0} to arrest her kidnapper,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:05.93,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,and he just {\i1}happened{\i0} to be the guy \Nwho killed Morofushi's parents in the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:06.99,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:08.37,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:11.92,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's an absurd excuse for skipping out \Non your cleaning duties to leave campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:12.99,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.86,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If that bathroom's still dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:20.77,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the bathroom itself \Nthat really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:22.50,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's not clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.72,0:23:29.05,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better keep this up all week!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:29.88,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:36.18,DCItalic,REI,0000,0000,0000,,I bought them time, just like I was told to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:41.11,DCItalic,REI,0000,0000,0000,,But I would've preferred to do this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:24:09.01,DCEpPreview,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:50.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So he has a criminal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:54.99,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He was serving time \Nin prison until last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:57.62,DCMain,CHIBA,0000,0000,0000,,This belongs to you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.70,DCMain,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:04.79,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's a 30-minute \Ngap between these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:09.01,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:15.01,DCNextEp,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiral of Rain and Malice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:13.20,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan \Nis "The Spiral of Rain and Malice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:34.95,Hint,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Earrings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:32.80,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:34.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.95,Don'tMiss,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:36.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's almost Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.53,0:24:37.54,DCMain,REI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Welcome back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.54,0:24:38.76,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You get to see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.76,0:24:39.60,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah.
